Class CadastroResponsavelController

java.lang.Object
controllers.CadastroResponsavelController
public class CadastroResponsavelController extends Object
Classe intermediaria que servira para ligar as telas disponiveis no package view com as classes disponiveis na package controller.
Author:
Izabella Alves Pereira, Lucas de Oliveira Dias Marques Ferreira
